@startuml
title Data Flow Diagram - Level 0 (Context Diagram)

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam padding 10

' External Entities
rectangle "Gym Owner\n(Admin)" as owner #FFD54F
rectangle "Gym Staff\n(Staff)" as staff #FFF176

' System
circle "GyMMS\nGym Membership\nManagement\nSystem" as system #4CAF50

' Layout positioning
owner -[hidden]down- staff

' Data Flows - Owner to System (Admin permissions)
owner -right-> system : Member & Staff management
owner -right-> system : Payment processing
owner -right-> system : System configuration

' Data Flows - System to Owner (Admin reports)
system -left-> owner : Dashboard & Analytics
system -left-> owner : Financial reports
system -left-> owner : Audit logs & Alerts

' Data Flows - Staff to System (Staff permissions)
staff -right-> system : Member information
staff -right-> system : Payment processing
staff -right-> system : Check-in/out requests

' Data Flows - System to Staff (Staff views)
system -left-> staff : Member status
system -left-> staff : Payment confirmations
system -left-> staff : Dashboard views

note right of system
  **Single Process View**
  All system functionality
  encapsulated as one process
  
  Owner: Full admin access
  Staff: Limited permissions
end note

@enduml
